data.text: @THEVinceRusso @PodcastOne @people Really?! You seemed to do a hell of a lot of judging in the podcast to all the other moms other then Jenelle. Sad.

@PodcastOne @THEVinceRusso @people Explain to me why we care, she is a product of what is wrong with our society at large. Thanks lending credence to it. Wee bit o sarcasm there in case you didn’t understand that

@PodcastOne @people I respect Jenelle for being honest and candid in our interview. We are all screw ups, we all make mistakes. Do I condone it-of course not-but, I don't judge either. We need to make mistakes and learn from them to become better people. I think Jenelle has.
